data.title: WTC Rotterdam
data.text:
World Trade Center Rotterdam has 51,500 m2 of office space divided over 6 floors in the Meent Offices & Coolsingel Offices and 23 floors in High Rise Offices, the 90 meter tall tower. Given its exceptional architecture and rich history, World Trade Center Rotterdam is a National Monument. The WTC Rotterdam building is perfectly finished and its service outstanding. Without exception, our tenants are dynamic and growing companies. We accommodate both well-known names and local starters. We lease office space to corporate and creative companies. We also have space for several business travelers and expats who rent a spot at WTC Rotterdam.

The World Trade Centers Association is a global platform with no fewer than 320 branches worldwide. The organisation promotes international trade and offers access to an international network that brings together like-minded entrepreneurs and professionals. As one of the founding members, WTC Rotterdam is proud to be part of this ambitious platform. Our goal is to serve as a regional platform for international business.

For questions about international trade and investments, our partners are there to help. This service evolved from a close collaboration of WTC Rotterdam, World Trade Center Netherlands Alliance, Rotterdam Partners and Innovation Quarter.

The committed and future-oriented Bouwinvest team focuses on creating real value for life. Together with their partners, Bouwinvest is helping to give shape to the city of the future. The Bouwinvest approach to real estate investment management contributes towards sustainable, liveable and accessible urban environments, and improves pension benefits. In doing so, Bouwinvest creates both societal and financial returns.
